3.2 New Help Request Algorithms
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As explain in RASD i assume that when there is a big accident somone call
 police or hospital.
 Usually there is an operator that answer to help requests and must advice
 his/her collegues in order to permit a rapid rescue.
 When he/she answer to help request he/she must take note about main information
 (place of accident, people injured, dangerous situation...) and these actions
 will be done with a PC.
 The information will be send directly to collegues, but also to system
 that will check if there will be some similar record in the DB.
 First discrimination will be done on hour
\end_layout

